Jason Rohde is accused of killing his wife Susan in July 2016. CAPE TOWN - Jason Rohde has begun the third day of testimony at his murder trial. The property mogul is accused of strangling Susan Rohde in their hotel room at the Spier Hotel near Stellenbosch, where they were for a work function. Rohde claims his spouse of 23 years committed suicide by hanging herself with a hair iron cord. Rohde claims he started having an affair with a co-worker in 2015. WATCH: Jason Rohde testimony courtesy of News24 